high_descs: Turn left to reach the diningtable.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Move the tomato to the middle of the table.
Cut the tomato on the table with the knife.
Turn around to walk down the passage on the left and head to the bedroom on the left to reach the tomato.
Cut the tomato on the bed with the knife.
Put the knife on the bed.
Pick up the tomato from the bed.
Turn around to head out of the bedroom and walk down the passage on the right and reach the kitchen on the left to head to the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
Turn around to exit the kitchen and head to the living room diningtable across the room.
Pick up the tomato from the table.
Head to the kitchen on the left to reach the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put two slices of Tomato in the Microwave.

high_descs: turn around and walk to the front of the diningtable.
pick up the knife from the table.
Stand up in front of the tomato.
Cut the tomato that is on the table.
leave the room and go to the bedroom.
Cut the tomato on the cutting board.
Put the knife down on the bed.
pick up a piece of the tomato.
take the tomato to the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
turn around and go into the living room
get one slice of tomato that is on the coffee table.
take the tomato with you to the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Get slices of tomato to put in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the longer side of the oval diningtable and turn to face it slightly on the left.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Move a tiny bit to the right to be in front of the tomato.
Cut the tomato with the knife.

Turn left, walk straight parallel to the wall on your left, turn left when to walk around the wall to a corridor, take the second entrance to a room and go to the opposite corner to see a tomato on a bed.
Cut the tomato on the bed with the knife.
Put the knife down on the bed.
Pick up the tomato slice from the bed.
Head back through the corridor but instead of going right to the oval table, go left to a kitchen corner, specifically the microwave in the upper right corner.
Put the tomato slice in the microwave.
Go to the diningtable where you left sliced tomato.
Pick up a tomato slice from the table.
Get back to the microwave.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Get two Tomato slices in the Microwave
